==English==
===Adjective===
'''write-in'''
# (''Of a candidate or campaign'') Without having the [[candidate]]'s name listed on the [[ballot]], requiring the [[voter]] to "write in" the candidate's name.

===Noun===
'''write-in'''
# A candidate whose name is not listed on the [[ballot]]
# A vote made for a candidate who is a [[write-in]].

